  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to evaluate the efficacy of Seprafilm and guardix in reducing the
      incidence of bowel obstruction and to evaluate the incidence of all serious adverse events
      (SAEs) associated with the use of Seprafilm and guardix occurring within 30 days
      postoperatively.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
