  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Clinical diagnosis of GI cancer

          -  Operable

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Withdrew consent

          -  Pregnant

          -  Ascites

          -  Distant metastasis

          -  Liver dysfunction (serum total bilirubin &gt;2.0 mg/dL)

          -  Renal failure (serum creatinine &gt;1.5 mg/dL)

          -  A past history of small bowel obstruction.
      </textblock>
